    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously preserved by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single blemish, and the interior is pristine, featuring leather that looks and smells brand new. Mechanically, the car is flawless, delivering a whisper-quiet ride and peak performance that mirrors its day-one state. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that requires absolutely no compromises.",
