    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with great potential? This car is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a solid foundation and a classic style that's hard to find. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to own a diamond in the rough and customize it exactly how you want!",
